<h2 class="p1"><b>Family , friends and co-workers gather together at Los Angeles Police Department Scientific Investigation Division to honor the memory of Forensic Print Specialist and Engineers and Architects Union Steward Anthony "Tony" Ortiz.Â </b></h2>
[slider][slide]http://eaaunion.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/NDT0012-2.jpg[/slide]

